0 -12 Td
(Bridge flow:) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
(1. Social or YME events are generated inside the Yenkasa app backend.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(2. `src/yme/services/eventPublisher.service.js` ingests the local YME event.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(3. The same publisher maps eligible events to intelligence events.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(4. `src/intelligence/services/eventPublisher.service.js` sends them to the YenkasaAi ) Tj
0 -12 Td
(backend.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(5. The YenkasaAi backend receives them on `POST /api/events` or `POST /api/events/ingest`.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(6. The YenkasaAi backend records the event and asynchronously processes it into YME memory ) Tj
0 -12 Td
(and analytics state.) Tj
